Level and Index

MultilevelEstimators.Level — Type.
Level(l::Integer)

Return a level.

Examples

julia> level = Level(2)
2

See also: Index

source
MultilevelEstimators.Index — Type.
Index(i::Integer...)

Return a multi-index.

Examples

julia> index = Index(2, 1)
(2, 1)

See also: Level
